export const clockColors = {
  colorWhenUsedForHoursAndMinutes:  'rgb(243, 146, 0)', //orange
  colorWhenUsedForHours :  'rgb(118, 184, 42)', //green
  colorWhenUsedForMinutes:  'rgb(0, 179, 217)', // blue
  colorWhenNotUsed: 'rgb(255, 255, 255)',
  singleClockBackGroundColor: 'rgb(255, 255, 255)',
  clockBackGroundColorArrayStartColor: 'rgb(255, 255, 255)',
  clockBackGroundColorArrayEndColor: 'rgb(0, 179, 217)',
  secondsCounterColor1: 'rgb(0, 179, 217)',
  secondsCounterColor2: 'rgb(118, 184, 42)'

}
